And there's a reason for that.

00:14:01.940 --> 00:14:03.740
I tend to notice
that most books that

00:14:03.740 --> 00:14:06.980
talk-- most books
about fishing, that

00:14:06.980 --> 00:14:09.480
mention fishing in any way--
there's a lot more than fishing

00:14:09.480 --> 00:14:09.980
in here.

00:14:09.980 --> 00:14:13.190
There's sea weeds and clams
and mussels and everything.

00:14:13.190 --> 00:14:15.350
But there's a lot of
fish talk in here.

00:14:15.350 --> 00:14:17.400
And most books that
talk about fishing,

00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:21.850
I just find them
terribly boring,

00:14:21.850 --> 00:14:25.000
because it's usually about how
do you catch the biggest fish.

