them to get to the clean ones.

00:41:40.020 --> 00:41:42.020
I mean there's hella clams
in San Francisco Bay,

00:41:42.020 --> 00:41:43.940
but no one in their right
mind would eat them,

00:41:43.940 --> 00:41:46.724
