sport fishing license.

00:42:13.926 --> 00:42:16.720
And you can take this book
and it will really help you.

00:42:16.720 --> 00:42:19.490
And then seaweed, I cover
all the basic seaweeds

00:42:19.490 --> 00:42:20.850
along our shoreline.

00:42:20.850 --> 00:42:22.610
Again, you should
get a fishing license

00:42:22.610 --> 00:42:24.942
if you're going to do seaweed.

00:42:24.942 --> 00:42:26.650
A lot of people think
they don't need it,

00:42:26.650 --> 00:42:28.340
but you should have that.

00:42:28.340 --> 00:42:32.280
It's like $50, and it's good for
the year in which you buy it.

00:42:32.280 --> 00:42:35.760
